Senegal
April 17 2020
First article. - The compulsory wearing of a protective mask during the state of emergency is prescribed in the following places:

    public administration services regardless of the management mode;
    private sector services;
    places of commerce;
    methods of transportation.

Article 2: Any breach of these provisions will be punished by the penalties provided for by the laws and regulations.

