First article. - The compulsory wearing of a protective mask for a period of three (03) months is prescribed, in order to limit the spread of the disease of COVID-19, in the following public and private places:

    public administration services regardless of the management mode;
    private sector services;
    places of commerce;
    methods of transportation.

Art. 2. - This decree will be published in the Official Journal.

