First article. - In order to limit the spread of the coronavirus, is prescribed for a period of three (03) months, throughout the national territory, the compulsory wearing of protective mask in the following public and private places:

    public roads ;
    public administration services regardless of the management mode;
    private sector services;
    places of commerce;
    public means of transport;
    means of private transport carrying at least two (02) people.

Article 2. - This decree will be published in the Official Journal. UPDATE: In January the policy was further extended by another 3 months

